      "rationale": "FDA-validated Ansys Mechanical release with documented V&V test suite; version-controlled simulation scripts archived in institutional repository. Software QA procedures conform to FDA guidance on software validation for computational tools."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
